# Production server (VPS)

- **Shell access to production**: use the host alias **`vps`** — the command is **`ssh vps`** (SSH config entry, not a literal hostname).
- When suggesting deploy checks, logs, or server commands, assume the user reaches the box with **`ssh vps`** unless they specify otherwise.
- Do not invent a different SSH target for "production" unless the user explicitly names one.
